You know how there's an Assist Core
called Opening Art?

rows.label: tlk43700241_03_msg0002
rows.name:
If I had that equipped and I got the
initiative, I'd have taken down the
Holy Grail before she could even blink...

rows.label: tlk43700241_03_msg0003
rows.name: Wait, why am I even telling you this?!

rows.label: tlk43700241_03_msg0004
rows.name:
And here I thought I had the perfect
comeback plan...

rows.label: tlk43700241_03_msg0005
rows.name:
But now that I've told you, I'll have
to scrap that idea. Well, back to the
drawing board...
